{"tid":1360801,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國駐港領事館發出外遊公告","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:27:36.000Z","uid":56590,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5565d9d1a0bc1e6ae94fbf7b5adab90d41653be","tid":1360801,"uid":56590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GDLinKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGDLinKh.jpg&h=82e9520f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98CTV4h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98CTV4h.jpg&h=46072617&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大致內容如下<br />\n(上網譯未必完全準確,請見諒)<br />\n<br />\n1.目前香港要求撒回送中條例及不滿港府措施的相關示威仍在繼續。特別是21日在元朗區發生多名男性攻擊示威人仕, 導致45人受傷的事件, 韓國國民需要注意。<br />\n<br />\n2.在香港停留的韓國國民請盡量避免前往示威地點, 如果不得已必須訪問示威地點附近,請參考以下事項,注意人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n○ 穿黑衣戴口罩時, 可能會被誤認爲是示威者。<br />\n○ 於示威中拍攝時, 可能會刺激示威群眾。<br />\n○ 可能遇到嚴重的交通堵塞及通訊干擾。<br />\n○ 可能發生主要景區及商店等暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n3.到目前爲止獲悉的示威計劃如下, 但請參考示威地點和時間可能會變動。<br />\n19.7.27 或 19.7.28 元朗 <br />\n19.8.17 紅磡或土瓜灣 <br />\n<br />\n4.我們領事館會繼續在網站上更新示威日程及安全守則等相關信息。 發生緊急情況時請與領事館及國內領事緊急中心聯繫。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://overseas.mofa.go.kr/hk-ko/brd/m_1499/view.do?seq=1345922&amp;fbclid=IwAR1ThxuHbwLPgl13kUZWcg1LtAIkoNmcsdWqvfE3AyZyTABXqFHyanoeK0A#facebookM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foverseas.mofa.go.kr%2Fhk-ko%2Fbrd%2Fm_1499%2Fview.do%3Fseq%3D1345922%26fbclid%3DIwAR1ThxuHbwLPgl13kUZWcg1LtAIkoNmcsdWqvfE3AyZyTABXqFHyanoeK0A%23facebookM&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9QWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=b50df1dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://overseas.mofa.go.kr/hk-ko/brd/m_1499/view.do?seq=1345922&amp;fbclid=IwAR1ThxuHbwLPgl13kUZWcg1LtAIkoNmcsdWqvfE3AyZyTABXqFHyanoeK0A#facebookM</a>"},{"pid":"273fc96aa6f1eb2868f91ac39ad491d47d129388","tid":1360801,"uid":41035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655aee62aed3f70c3209d3838c289753d0bb699b","tid":1360801,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95296f5a732922cffc65f45a525a2f793579b9dc","tid":1360801,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}